            <h5>4. KEEP YOUR FEET INSULATED.</h5>
            <p class="ceg-b32">
                Finding a great pair of winter boots is only half the battle. The socks you choose to layer with your boots can help your feet stay even warmer. Pick thick, wool socks if you have room. Ankle-length socks are best to wear with boots to help keep them in place.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row ce-mobile-full ce-mobile-collapse">
